data.description: Wow! Show-stopping fully remodeled home in the heart of Uptown. Open floor plan with great flow. The kitchen takes center stage with generous island, quartz countertops, gas range, stainless steel appliances, wine fridge & soft close cabinetry. 4 beds, 3 bath with 2 car garage. Recent updates include: Roof, HVAC, Electrical, Plumbing, Windows, Flooring & more. Luxurious primary suite with huge walk-in double shower, dual vanity, private WC and walk-in closet. Grassy backyard with custom shade pergola, RV gate and room for a pool. Neighborhood has an abundance of restaurants & shopping, convenient to highways, downtown and Scottsdale. In the heart of the action, yet nestled in a quiet walkable neighborhood. Swing Set conveys. Madison School Dist. NO HOA. Assumable 2.75% VA loan
